<subSubSection id="C37F65649400FFDABACF3E52FD28FAE0" pageId="15" pageNumber="266" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8BDA36EF9400FFDABACF3E52FC64FAA8" blockId="15.[151,1437,896,2039]" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">
<emphasis id="B911EAFD9400FFDABACF3E52FEC3FBD8" bold="true" box="[199,350,1111,1138]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">Type locality.</emphasis>
<materialsCitation id="3B0D3CB29400FFDABB6D3E52FC68FAA8" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3750350348" collectorName="Hence, I &amp; F. Sello" country="Uruguay" county="Uruguayan" location="Suffrian's" municipality="On" pageId="15" pageNumber="266" specimenCount="1" stateProvince="Colonia" typeStatus="lectotype">
<collectingRegion id="49A1F80D9400FFDABB6D3E52FDECFBD8" box="[357,625,1112,1138]" country="Uruguay" name="Colonia" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">Colonia del Sacramento</collectingRegion>
(
<collectingRegion id="49A1F80D9400FFDAB8883E52FD40FBD8" box="[640,733,1112,1138]" country="Uruguay" name="Colonia" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">Colonia</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F372767F9400FFDAB8EF3E53FCD3FBD9" box="[743,846,1113,1139]" name="Uruguay" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">Uruguay</collectingCountry>
). 
<location id="8EBA60349400FFDAB9683E52FC53FBD8" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03CC87F99400FFC4BA9F38B8FAB1F933:8EBA60349400FFDAB9683E52FC53FBD8" box="[864,974,1112,1138]" country="Uruguay" county="Uruguayan" municipality="On" name="Suffrian's" pageId="15" pageNumber="266" stateProvince="Colonia">Suffrian’s</location>
indications regarding the localities of the type series are often rather generic. 
<location id="8EBA60349400FFDAB8223E77FDD6FB3D" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03CC87F99400FFC4BA9F38B8FAB1F933:8EBA60349400FFDAB8223E77FDD6FB3D" box="[554,587,1149,1175]" country="Uruguay" county="Uruguayan" municipality="On" name="He" pageId="15" pageNumber="266" stateProvince="Colonia">He</location>
seems to consider “Còl. del Sàcr.” to be a 
<location id="8EBA60349400FFDABE243E76FB0EFB3C" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03CC87F99400FFC4BA9F38B8FAB1F933:8EBA60349400FFDABE243E76FB0EFB3C" box="[1068,1171,1148,1174]" country="Uruguay" county="Uruguayan" municipality="On" name="Brazilian" pageId="15" pageNumber="266" stateProvince="Colonia">Brazilian</location>
toponym. 
<location id="8EBA60349400FFDABF043E77FAE9FB3D" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03CC87F99400FFC4BA9F38B8FAB1F933:8EBA60349400FFDABF043E77FAE9FB3D" box="[1292,1396,1149,1175]" country="Uruguay" county="Uruguayan" municipality="On" name="However" pageId="15" pageNumber="266" stateProvince="Colonia">However</location>
, no evidence was found regarding the existence of a place with a similar name in southern 
<collectingCountry id="F372767F9400FFDABE5D3EAAFB00FB10" box="[1109,1181,1184,1210]" name="Brazil" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. 
<collectingMunicipality id="6BBEAC959400FFDABEAF3EAAFB54FB10" box="[1191,1225,1184,1210]" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">On</collectingMunicipality>
the other hand, the name corresponds to a well-known 
<collectingCounty id="62BB4E639400FFDAB82C3ECFFD3DFB75" box="[548,672,1221,1247]" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">Uruguayan</collectingCounty>
locality. 
<collectorName id="269053399400FFDAB90E3ECFFCF8FB75" box="[774,869,1221,1247]" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">Hence, I</collectorName>
am inclined to think that the 
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9400FFDABEA33ECEFA8FFB74" box="[1195,1298,1220,1246]" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">lectotype</typeStatus>
comes from 
<collectingCountry id="F372767F9400FFDABA9F3EE3FF67FAA9" box="[151,250,1257,1283]" name="Uruguay" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">Uruguay</collectingCountry>
, where the collector, 
<collectorName id="269053399400FFDABBE13EE3FDDDFAA8" box="[489,576,1256,1283]" pageId="15" pageNumber="266">F. Sello</collectorName>
, travelled extensively (
<bibRefCitation id="EFF44B1E9400FFDAB94B3EE2FC70FAA8" author="Krausch, H. D." box="[835,1005,1256,1282]" pageId="15" pageNumber="266" pagination="73 - 76" refId="ref24875" refString="Krausch, H. D. (2002) Friedrich Sello, ein vergessener Pflanzensammler aus Potsdam. Zandera, 17 (2), 73 - 76." type="journal article" year="2002">Krausch, 2002</bibRefCitation>
)
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
